<h1> Spotify Followers Search</h1>

<p>
This app uses a background process to query Spotify's API for artists' followers, persisting that information to the database. 
</p>
<p>
A D3.js chart re-draws itself every second pulling the latest entry from the database. 
</p>
<div>
<%= form_tag("/artists#create", method: "post") do %>
  <%= submit_tag( "Search") %>
<% end %>
<div>
<p>
  <button class="pure-button pure-button-primary" onclick="dynamicBarChart();">Get Started</button>
  <div class="label" id="label"></div>
</p>




